                        option(value="0").activity__option Lorem ipsum, dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Id, est! 
                .activity__input.last 
                    p.activity__name Tell us more
                    textarea(name="textarea").activity__textarea
                p.activity__p Drop in any relevant files here
                <label for="file-upload" class="custom-file-upload">Select files</label>
                    <input id="file-upload" class="activity__input-file" type="file"/>
                p.activity__desc Information you submit here will be used as detailed in our privacy policy so we can get back to you. From time to time, we would like to contact you about news, insights and exclusive event invitations by email. If you would like to opt-in to receive these marketing emails please tick the relevant boxes below. You will be able to opt-out at any time using the links provided in our emails or by contacting us as detailed in our privacy policy.
                .activity__checkbox.first 
                    input(type="checkbox" id="checkbox1") 
                    label(for="checkbox1").activity__label I agree to receive a monthly creative community newsletter (Vimotion Production)
                .activity__checkbox 
                    input(type="checkbox" id="checkbox2") 
                    label(for="checkbox2").activity__label I want to be invited to The Mill’s Virtual Events & receive other marketing comms from Vimotion Production
                button(type="submit").activity__button Submit